'''Jory Cassel''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Jamie Sives]] and debuts in the [[Winter is Coming (episode)|series premiere]]. He is the captain of the guards to [[House Stark]]. He is killed by [[Jaime Lannister]] while defending Lord [[Eddard Stark]] in [[King's Landing]].

